\n失票達4500 門檻人數 -45人<br />\n<br />\n清算時間由呢個回覆起計至提名大會結束後即5月28日0時0分截止<br />\n杜小喬淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達75票<br />\n<br />\n陳穎欣@SG淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達115票<br />\n<br />\n麥明詩淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達165票<br />\n<br />\n黃翠如淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達160票<br />\n<br />\n陳庭欣淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達210票<br />\n<br />\n吳嘉熙淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達130票<br />\n<br />\n梁嘉琪淘汰條件:<br />\n正評&gt;負評<br />\n總參與票數達200票"},{"pid":"abc5cd8b91aee79400803bf59cf5b270e40ea3f2","tid":1157994,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"由大家作命運自決"},{"pid":"7b0d578e537f3343206bf66858155d770e680660","tid":1157994,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"多謝支持"},{"pid":"615134b5d1e18a2203223313b384d2448c7d7192","tid":1157994,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"提提大家<br />\n成功留低既意思就係佢會依照規例去降班<br />\n例如超聯 當麥明詩無比你地掟走<br />\n咁佢本身已經護級失敗 就會降班去冠聯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca86f19f9a1d4e1344e9a8bd4e5f63ce13f382be","tid":1157994,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"清清清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8736818025ca01e52ef6615df03436f2303a2c66","tid":1157994,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca86f19f9a1d4e1344e9a8bd4e5f63ce13f382be","tid":1157994,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"清清清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"某啲咁撚廢 公道講係應該踢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets